been building legs. We understand how to walk,

00:02:12.330 --> 00:02:15.470
we understand how to manipulate objects.

00:02:15.470 --> 00:02:19.540
So the big challenge for roboticists today
is how do we integrate all this component

00:02:19.540 --> 00:02:25.980
technology in a way that is reliable, that
is affordable and that gives us the functionality

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:28.380
approaching that of a human being.

